ted the house of a medical doctor in the area as they went straight to his residence and abducted him and 6 members of his family.” “They attacked other houses and abducted 9 other residents. An officer confirmed that the commander had been killed by the bandits.”  “They took his corpse to his wife and later buried him. We are just coming from the burial ground ,” he said.  “The situation could have been worse  but the people quickly informed neighbourin communities who came out and  chased the bandits.That was how we were able to rescue  6 kidnapped persons,”the source added. People in communities around the Millennium City Kaduna have been living in fear of bandit attacks, a situation that made some residents to  relocate to other locations for safety . Vanguard News Nigeria    Bandits raid community in Kaduna, kill JTF Commander, kidnap Medical doctor, others In "News" lKaduna confirms attack, debunks reports of aerial attack by terrorists lSays NAF helicopter arrived to engage bandits lBurn shops, food barns in Katsina By Ibrahim Hassan Bandits have again killed no fewer than 32 persons in four communities in Kajuru Local Government Area of Kaduna State. They also kidnapped at… In "Metro" File photo of terrorists By Ibrahim Hassan-Wuyo No fewer than 20 persons have been kidnapped in Kurmin Sata, a few kilometers from Millennium City in Chikun Local Government Area of Kaduna State. One person was also said to have been killed. Also, 10 farmers, who were cultivating on their farms… In "Metro"